Package com.cafean.rpc

Class RPCXdr

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.apt.xdr.Xdr
      • com.cafean.rpc.RPCXdr
  • public class RPCXdr
extends Xdr
    An selected set of Xdr routine overrides for use in situations where exceptions thrown during read routines must be handled by the calling methods.

    todo: determine whether to include support for UTF-8 and/or UTF-16 strings in readString/writeString
